    <h2>Main Activities</h2>
    <p>We provide emergency relief, medical assistance, and long-term support to communities affected by disasters and conflicts worldwide. Our efforts focus on improving access to food, water, healthcare, and education.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="approach">
    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <p>Our approach is rooted in collaboration and sustainability. We work closely with local communities, partner organizations, and governments to ensure that our aid reaches those in need effectively and efficiently. We prioritize long-term solutions, striving to empower communities and build resilience against future crises.</p>
  </section>

